algorithm_technique: Compare start and end times of two events to detect overlap.
problem_summary_simple: Determine if two time intervals overlap.
problem_summary_technical: Check for interval overlap by comparing the maximum start time with the minimum end time.
key_insights: Two intervals [a, b] and [c, d] overlap if max(a, c) <= min(b, d).
String comparison works directly for HH:MM format.
No complex data structures or algorithms are needed.
